        "text": "On the evening of October 24, 1950 I was attending a moving picture\nshow at the Oak Ridge out-door drive-in theater. I arrived approximately\nat 6:45 which was about 15 minutes prior to show time. While sitting in\nthe car with my wife and children I casually glanced skyward towards"
      },
